      Resources v2.0.0

      API for the nterprise application

      Terms of service

      License: MIT

      Authentication

      • HTTP Authentication, scheme: bearer

      Resource

      fetchAllResources

      GET /resources

      Fetches A Page of resources

      Fetch resources

      Parameters

      Name In Type Required Description
      limit query integer(int32) false How many items to return at one time (max 100)
      offset query string false Continue from last offset
      sort query string false Sort by field
      filter[resource_type] query string false Filter where the resource type is this value

      Enumerated Values

      Parameter Value
      sort label
      sort -label
      sort created
      sort -created
      sort updated
      sort -updated

      Responses

      Status Meaning Description Schema
      200 OK A paged response for resources Inline
      401 Unauthorized Unauthorized Inline
      403 Forbidden Forbidden Inline

      Response Schema

      Status Code 200

      Name Type Required Restrictions Description
      » _embedded object false none none
      »» nter:resources [allOf] false none none
      »»» _links object false none none
      »»»» self object false read-only none
      »»»»» href string false none none

      Status Code 401

      Name Type Required Restrictions Description
      » title any false none none
      » type any false none none
      » status any false none none
      » detail any false none none

      Status Code 403

      Name Type Required Restrictions Description
      » title any false none none
      » type any false none none
      » status any false none none
      » detail any false none none
      This operation does not require authentication

      fetchAllChildResources
